summary:
As an International Educator with a background in International Baccalaureate programme, I teach French language and culture and I am inspired by holistic learning, intercultural awareness and communication. 

My expertise lies in designing lessons for foreign language classes adapted to various levels and age groups.

Founder of Langue Virtuelle, language specialist at IB companions, I am currently a French lecturer at the International Business department of The Hague University of Applied sciences, where I also prepare students to be world citizens in a successful business career.
